1.What is Python ? What are the Ways to Install Python in your PC ?
A. Python is an Interpreted,Object-Oriented,High-Level programming language with dynamic semantics.
Python's simple, easy to learn syntax emphasizes readability and therefore reduces the cost of program maintenance.
It provides Huge amount of additional  Open-source libraries.
Installing:
  Download directly from python.org or download Anaconda
